# User Preferences (Example)

Copy this file to `user.md` and customize for your preferences.

## Environment

```bash
# Docker container name
CONTAINER=poyenc-ck

# Workspace path inside container
WORKSPACE=/root/workspace/worktree/aiter-main
```

## Preferences

- Preferred editor: vim
- Commit message style: conventional commits
- Do not add Co-Authored-By lines in commit messages
- Test command preferences: pytest with verbose output

## Notes

Add any personal notes or reminders here.
